      "span_text": "We then conducted 2 independent runs of 1,000,000 Markov chain Monte Carlo simulation steps. Consistent marginal peak locations with unimodal likelihood curves approaching 0 on either end of the distribution of parameter values indicated reasonable sampling of trees, which were then used in ''LoadTree'' mode to estimate joint distributions, final parameter estimates, and credibility intervals [CITATION_1] ."
